x zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3617238\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ysi1665702632806.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ysi1665702632806.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ysi1665702632806.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ysi1665702632806\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Focus Background Color (\n                              BackColorFocus)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Focus Background Color ( \n                                BackColorFocus) specifies the color of the background when the button field has focus.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ysi1665702632806__p_d103808e1_d103809e1_d103810e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>BackColorFocus<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var> |\n        <var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ysi1665702632806__table_d12239e1_d12240e1_d12241e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ysi1665702632806__table_d12239e1_d12240e1_d12241e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ysi1665702632806__table_d12239e1_d12240e1_d12241e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ysi1665702632806__table_d12239e1_d12240e1_d12241e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ysi1665702632806__table_d12239e1_d12240e1_d12241e1__entry__2\">Name of a web color or system color. For more\n                     information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rcm1665702587635.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rcm1665702587635.html\" title=\"Uniface supports standard color definitions including system colors as defined by the operating system, Web colors defined by the W3C, and RGB (red-green-blue) colors expressed in hex or decimal numbers. Any of these color definitions can be used when defining the value of foreground and background colors of components, widgets, panels, and toolbars.\">Standard Colors</a>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ysi1665702632806__table_d12239e1_d12240e1_d12241e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ysi1665702632806__table_d12239e1_d12240e1_d12241e1__entry__2\">Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of a\n                     color.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ysi1665702632806__section_ivl_mgn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d181386e126\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ysi1665702632806__table_d12242e1_d12243e1_d12244e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Representation</span> property\n                     must be set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ysi1665702632806__section_lqt_4gn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d181386e177\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ysi1665702632806__pre_qtl_rgn_wwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"aliceblue\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ysi1665702632806__section_bqr_rgn_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d181386e186\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrc1665702631553.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" title=\"The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.\">CommandButton</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/btj1665702631955.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Representation</a><p>This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617238\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617238\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Focus Background Color ( BackColorFocus) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Focus Background Color ( BackColorFocus) The Focus Background Color ( BackColorFocus) specifies the color of the background when the button field has focus. \" BackColorFocus = ColorName | HexColorNumber \" Value Description ColorName Name of a web color or system color. For more information, see Standard Colors . HexColorNumber Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of a color. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Representation property must be set to Uniface Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"aliceblue\" Copy Applies To CommandButton Related Links Representation This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}